        {
          "html": "<style>\n  :root {\n    --color-absolute-zero: #000000;\n    --color-studio-white: #ffffff;\n    --color-soft-gray: #f5f5f5;\n    --color-pale-border: #e0e0e0;\n    --color-ghost-gray: #737373;\n    --font-aktiv-grotesk: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  }\n</style>\n<div style=\"font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;\">\n  <!-- Dark Feature Block -->\n  <div style=\"background:var(--color-absolute-zero);padding:56px 40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n    <!-- Decorative music grid background suggestion -->\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:55%;height:100%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);grid-template-rows:repeat(4,1fr);gap:4px;opacity:0.35;pointer-events:none;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#4a3728;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#2d4a2d;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#1a2d4a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#4a1a2d;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#2d3a1a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#3a2d4a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#4a3a1a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#1a4a3a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#4a2d1a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#2d1a4a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#3a4a1a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#1a3a4a;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Content -->\n    <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:320px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"color:var(--color-studio-white);font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);font-size:40px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Descubre música nueva</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:var(--color-studio-white);font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 32px 0;opacity:0.9;\">No te pierdas las miles de emisoras en directo, la música seleccionada por expertos y el contenido original de Sonos Radio.</p>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:transparent;color:var(--color-studio-white);font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid var(--color-studio-white);border-radius:80px;padding:16px 40px;cursor:pointer;\">Obtener información</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Light Feature Card -->\n  <div style=\"background:var(--color-soft-gray);padding:40px;border-radius:10px;margin-top:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;\">\n    <!-- Image placeholder -->\n    <div style=\"width:100%;height:200px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c8c0b8 0%,#8a8078 50%,#4a3830 100%);border-radius:10px;\"></div>\n    <div>\n      <h3 style=\"color:var(--color-absolute-zero);font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);font-size:32px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">Descubre Sonos Play.</h3>\n      <p style=\"color:var(--color-absolute-zero);font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 24px 0;opacity:0.75;\">Un imponente sonido estéreo con graves profundos en un formato fácil de transportar.</p>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:transparent;color:var(--color-absolute-zero);font-family:var(--font-aktiv-grotesk);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid var(--color-absolute-zero);border-radius:80px;padding:14px 36px;cursor:pointer;\">Obtener información</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
